{}.response: The main characters of the TV show 'New Girl' include Jessica Day, who is an offbeat and adorable girl in her late 20s; Nick Miller, a law school dropout who now works as a bartender; Schmidt, an over-confident ladies' man who works in marketing; Winston Bishop, a competitive former basketball player who struggles to find his footing after playing professionally overseas; and Cece Parekh, Jessica's best friend since childhood who is a fashion model. The dynamics among these friends make up the heart of the show as they navigate relationships, careers, and personal growth.
